Information Retrival from the SB277 hearings via DigitalDemocracy
(http://www.digitaldemocracy.org/bill/201520160SB277).

Jeff McGovern - jmcgover@calpoly.edu
Nicole Martin - nlmartin@calpoly.edu

To show usage and all supported arguments, run the following on the command line: 
./run.py -h

Processing and querying is a 2-step process via run.py
1) supply the utterances JSON with or without stemming and stopword options
2) use the pickle file produced in step 1 with a query.txt to retrieve info

